name: skymansionx/Image-Processing-Service
description: 🖼️ Image Processing Service: An API for performing common image manipulations like resizing, watermarking, and applying filters. ✂️ A useful microservice for many applications. 🎨

name: skymansionx/Simple-Physics-Engine
description: 🧪 Simple Physics Engine: A basic 2D physics engine implementing fundamental concepts like gravity. 📐 Simulates momentum and collision response in a 2D environment. Great for simulations. 💥 🎮

name: skymansionx/Whac-A-Mole
description: 🔨 Quick Reaction Arcade: A digital Whac-A-Mole game. ⚡ Excellent for practicing responsive DOM manipulation and precise input timing. Test your reflexes! ⏱️ 🎯

name: skymansionx/Tactical-RPG
description: 🧠 Tactical RPG: A grid combat RPG featuring turn-based combat on a grid-based map. ⚔️ Focuses on positioning, range calculation, and complex ability trees. Learn advanced game logic! 🛡️ 🗡️

name: skymansionx/Mobile-App-Template-Kit
description: 📱 Mobile-App-Template-Kit: A boilerplate project for building mobile apps that run on both iOS and Android. ⚡ Uses a framework like React Native or Flutter. 🚀

name: skymansionx/Action-Adventure-Game
description: 💥 Action-Adventure Game: A combat & exploration game featuring real-time combat. 🗺️ Includes inventory management and exploration mechanics across a defined world. ⚔️ 🧭

name: skymansionx/Dotfiles-Manager
description: 🗄️ Dotfiles Manager: A script and repository for managing personal configuration files (.bashrc, .vimrc, etc.) across multiple machines. 💻 Keeps your setup consistent. ⚙️

name: skymansionx/Web-Scraper-for-E-commerce
description: 🛒 Web Scraper for E-commerce: An e-commerce scraper designed to extract product information. 🔍 Gathers pricing and availability from online stores. Focuses on automated data extraction. 📊 🌐

name: skymansionx/Labyrinth-Explorer-3D
description: 🧭 Labyrinth-Explorer-3D: A 3D Maze Game where the player navigates a randomly generated maze from a first-person perspective. Focuses on camera control and environment rendering. 💡

name: skymansionx/Grid-Matrix-Game
description: 🧱 Grid Matrix Game: A meticulous adaptation of Tetris. 🧠 Focuses on complex block rotation, line clearing logic, and high-performance rendering. ⚙️

name: skymansionx/Measurement-Converter-Kit
description: ⚖️ Measurement-Converter-Kit: A Unit Converter Tool that handles various measurements (weight, volume, distance) with high precision and customizable units. Perfect for utility development. 💾
